## 写操作必须记录审计日志

所有涉及 customers / equipments / work_orders 的新增、修改、删除，
必须调用 `from core.audit import write_audit_log`：

```python
write_audit_log(
    db=db,
    user_id=operator_id,
    action="CREATE",        # CREATE / UPDATE / DELETE
    table_name="customers",
    record_id=customer.customer_id,
    new_value=data,         # 变更后数据快照
)
```

